# Coinc
Coinc is an Alfred workflow which do currency conversion by using live currency rates from Open Exchange Rates API. For a complete list of support currencies, see [Currencies](https://github.com/tomy0000000/Coinc/blob/master/Currencies.md).
For comprehensive Installation and Usage, see [Wiki](https://github.com/tomy0000000/Coinc/wiki)
